oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Hot Summer Nights Concert Series
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Woodcuts (prints); Clowns;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (blue and pink on white) announcing the Hot Summer Night Concert Series at Camden Park featuring Brother Smith on July 12 and 13, Nora Jane Struthers on July 19, and the Tillers on July 26 and 27. Poster features woodcuts of a carnival scene and a clown.
